  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this activity is for students to solve an area problem that involves missing side lengths. The problem has multiple solutions, as the area of the garden could be between 20 square feet to 30 square feet. The launch serves to familiarize students with the ideas involved in designing a garden before they solve the problem.</p>
<p>When students share with other groups and describe what others did that was different they are making and understanding mathematical arguments (MP3).</p>
<p>This activity uses MLR6 Three Reads. Advances: reading, listening, representing</p>
  </paragraphs>


